  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Empowering small cotton farmers and cotton pickers in South Punjab</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The focus area for this project is the district of Muzaffargar in South Punjab. This project will directly benefit 10,000 marginalised cotton growers and cotton pickers &#x2013; 90 per cent of the beneficiaries will be women and girls. Indirectly, the project will impact more than 25,000 people &#x2013; the families of the farmers and pickers, and community members who will benefit from the stimulation of the local economy, and increased awareness of the conditions that workers in the cotton industry are facing.</narrative>
  </description>
